---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Blog - Gil Gatson"
  description="Insights on technology, geopolitics, business strategy, and entrepreneurship from Gil Gatson."
>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Blog</h1>
    
    <p class="intro">
      Insights on technology, geopolitics, business strategy, and entrepreneurship.
    </p>
    
    <div class="blog-grid">
      <article class="blog-card">
        <h2><a href="/blog/america-losing-ai-race">Why America Is Losing the AI Race to China</a></h2>
        <p class="meta">Coming Soon</p>
        <p>
          An analysis of the five strategic bottlenecks strangling American AI development and how China is gaining ground through disciplined industrial strategy.
        </p>
      </article>
      
      <article class="blog-card">
        <h2><a href="/blog/energy-infrastructure-ai">Energy Infrastructure: The Hidden Constraint on AI Development</a></h2>
        <p class="meta">Coming Soon</p>
        <p>
          Why data centers need massive amounts of electricity, and how America's energy infrastructure compares to China's nuclear reactor buildout.
        </p>
      </article>
      
      <article class="blog-card">
        <h2><a href="/blog/open-source-trap">The Open Source Trap: How America Is Helping Its Rivals</a></h2>
        <p class="meta">Coming Soon</p>
        <p>
          The unintended consequences of open-source AI development from a national security perspective.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
    
    <div class="coming-soon">
      <p>üìù Blog posts coming soon. Check back for regular updates on AI, geopolitics, and business strategy.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .intro {
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--color-gray);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }
    
    .blog-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    
    .blog-card {
      padding: 2rem;
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    
    .blog-card:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    .blog-card h2 {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .blog-card h2 a {
      color: var(--color-text);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    .blog-card h2 a:hover {
      color: var(--color-accent);
    }
    
    .meta {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--color-gray);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .coming-soon {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: #f9fafb;
      border-radius: 8px;
      color: var(--color-gray);
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
